    <title>DMC-S1000DBIKE-AAA-DA2-20-00-00AA-720A-A_011-00_EN-US</title>
    <introduction>
        <para>The following document provides the guidelines for the installation of a handlebar on a mountain bicycle.</para>
    </introduction>
